// Shader:   3dGlassWithCaustic.glsl   2018-11-23
//
// original: https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XljGWR by andregc
//
// Distance function, camera setup and base for raymarching
//           https://www.shadertoy.com/view/Xds3zN by IQ
